# orderedDocuments

**Instance Property**

An array of document objects arranged according to the front-to-back ordering of their associated windows.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var orderedDocuments: [NSDocument] { get }
```

## Scripting your app

- **orderedWindows**: An array of window objects arranged according to their front-to-back ordering on the screen.
